Process Overview : HARDWARE

Step-1: Dismantling the Wheelchair
Remove unnecessary parts to prepare for motor installation.

Step-2: Dismantling the Hoverboard
Extract hub motors and other usable components from the hoverboard.

Step-3: Fitting Wheelchair with Hoverboard Motors
Attach hub motors to the wheelchair for powered mobility.

Step-4: Connecting Motor Controllers to Motors
Wire motor controllers to the hub motors for operational control.

Step-5: Connecting Arduino to Motor Controllers
Interface Arduino with motor controllers for signal processing and command execution.

Step-6: Connecting Battery to Motor Controllers
Power the system by connecting a suitable battery to the motor controllers.

Step-7: Connecting Laptop to Arduino
Establish a connection between the laptop and Arduino for data transfer and control.

